                <div class="col-12 d-block d-md-none animated invisible delay-3" data-animation="fadeInUp">
                    <img src="/assets/images/main/sections/sc-prtests-figure.png" class="d-block img-fluid mx-auto mb-4" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 d-block d-md-none">
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-center align-items-center gap-2">
                        <div class="pill">
                            <span class="pill-header">Simulación del examen</span>
                            <span class="pill-contents">Practica en un entorno similar al examen oficial y familiarízate con su formato.</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pill">
                            <span class="pill-header">Feedback inmediato</span>
                            <span class="pill-contents">Obtén resultados al instante con estadísticas e informes de progreso.</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pill">
